  : 50CONFIG

  \ ----------------------------------------------
  \ Set number of video frames for each game frame
  \ ----------------------------------------------

  1 FrameRate !L

  \ A setting of 1 will give the fastest possible game, which runs each game
  \ frame exactly in time with the video refresh rate.  On slower Amigas
  \ this speed will not be attainable when many objects are on screen, and
  \ the gameplay will slow down unacceptably in such circumstances.
  \
  \ This setting will give the best smooth scrolling and very smooth fast
  \ object movements, but requires at least a 25mhz CPU.
  \
  \ A setting of 2 will only run one game frame once every two video frames.
  \ This allows twice as much time for the Amiga to carry out the processing
  \ of each game frame, and will allow the gameplay to run at normal speed
  \ even on slower Amigas.
  \
  \ This setting will give a slightly jerky scrolling and somewhat blurred
  \ object movement.
  \

  \ -------------------------------------------------------
  \ Create framerate dependent game configuration variables
  \ -------------------------------------------------------

  12   ShotSpeed            !  \ Horizontal speed of Shots
  8    HumanoidFrameSpeed   !  \ Speed of Humanoid animation frames
  50   HumanoidSafeTime     !  \ Time before restored humanoid is vulnerable
  1    LanderMaxSpeed       !  \ Lander speed limit
  50   ResumeDelay          !  \ Safety period after materialisation
  50   ShipLaunchTime       !  \ Length of ship fade-in/out
  10   ShipLaunchWait       !  \ Length of ship fade-in/out speedchange
  30   ExFadeTime           !  \ Length of explosion fade phase
  8    ExFadeSpeed          !  \ Speed of particles on fade phase
  10   ExBurstTime          !  \ Length of explosion burst phase
  8    ExBurstSpeed         !  \ Speed of particles on burst phase
  4    ExBurstGrowth        !  \ Explosion burst phase growth rate
  30   FirePeriod           !  \ Laser "autofire" recharge period
  25   FireDelay            !  \ Laser "autofire" delay
  6    LanderAnimSpeed      !  \ Speed of Lander animation
  2    LanderAnimExpSpeed   !  \ Speed of Lander explosion animation
  20   LanderAnimExptime    !  \ Duration of Lander explosion
  1    LanderAnimIntroSpeed !  \ Speed of Lander "intro" animation
